**Summary:** This documentation covers the Amplitude Python SDK (amplitude-analytics package) for sending events to Amplitude, including installation via pip, client initialization with API key, configuration options like flush_queue_size and flush_interval_millis, event tracking with BaseEvent, user properties management via Identify operations, user groups with set_group(), group properties with group_identify(), revenue tracking with Revenue interface, and plugin system for enrichment and destination types.

